OL,3,CUniversity academics announce 14 days
OL,4,Cof strike action next month
OL,6,FStaff at Newcastle University will
OL,7,Fstrike for 14 days in March the
OL,8,FUniversity and College Union (UCU)
OL,9,Fsaid today (Friday 14 February).
OL,11,FThe dispute is over a threat to cut
OL,12,Fmore than #30m which could lead to
OL,13,Faround 300 job losses.
OL,15,FStaff are expected to picket outside
OL,16,Funiversity buildings each day of the
OL,17,Ffollowing strike days:
OL,19,FWeek 1: Tuesday 4 and Thursday 6 March
