OL,3,CUniversity academics announce 14 days
OL,4,Cof strike action next month
OL,6,FMatt Perry, branch chair of the UCU
OL,7,FNewcastle branch, said: "Our members
OL,8,Fare angry that Newcastle University's
OL,9,Fvice-chancellor, the chair of the
OL,10,FRussell Group of 'research-intensive'
OL,11,Funiversities, is increasing the
OL,12,Funiversity's carbon footprint during a
OL,13,Fstaff travel ban with talk of a new
OL,14,Fcampus halfway across the world.
OL,16,F"He should be sat with us at the
OL,17,Fnegotiating table. He now has two
OL,18,Fweeks to protect jobs and resolve this
OL,19,Fdispute to avoid sustained strike
OL,20,Faction across campus."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
