OL,3,CUniversity academics announce 14 days
OL,4,Cof strike action next month
OL,6,FNewcastle University is not the only
OL,7,Finstitution to face strikes, with
OL,8,Fstaff at the University of Dundee,
OL,9,FUniversity of East Anglia, Sheffield
OL,10,FHallam amongst others also expecting
OL,11,Fto have industrial action take place
OL,12,Fthis spring.
OL,14,FUCU general secretary Jo Grady said:
OL,15,F"Across the country, our members are
OL,16,Fclear that students and staff should
OL,17,Fnot have to pay the price, in course
OL,18,Fclosures and ruined livelihoods, for
OL,19,Fvice-chancellors' inability to manage
OL,20,Ffinances.
